Framework exceptions.

          Description

Exception Summary
AttributeAccessException Exception for attribute access errors.
ExecutionException Exception in the execution of a method.
InitializingException Exception in the initialization of an object.
NoApplicableFilterPredicateException Trying to apply a similarity function to an incompatible attribute
NoApplicableSimilarityFunctionException Trying to apply a similarity function to an incompatible attribute
OntologyAccessException Error accessing an ontology (using OntoBridge).
UnImplementedException Exception thrown when something is not implemented yet.
